## Maxima-cas can

```{maxima, echo=TRUE}
laplace(delta(t-2)*t, t, s);
ilt(2/(s^2-4),s,t);
expand(trigrat(sinh(2*t)));
partfrac(1/(s^2-4), s);
desolve([diff(y(t),t,3)-diff(y(t),t,2)-4*diff(y(t),t,1)+4*y(t)=exp(t)],[y(t)]);
```